"3  (4-oz.) bittersweet chocolate baking bars (60% cacao), chopped","2/3 cup strong-brewed coffee","1/4 cup bourbon","1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract","1/2 teaspoon reduced-sodium soy sauce","1 2/3 cups heavy cream, divided","1/4 cup sugar","  Store-bought shortbread cookies (optional)","  Toppings: sweetened whipped cream, fresh raspberries, chocolate shavings"